1.title: Master pizzas
1.plot: Not all pizzas are created equal so food obsessed is seeking out the sauciest, cheesiest, most delicious pizza concoctions ever created. We're going to be biting into everything.

2.title: Lard have mercy
2.plot: Food obsessed is diving headfirst into a giant vat of deep-fried deliciousness. We're sinking our teeth into everything from those southern staples to freaky fair food.

3.title: Say cheese!
3.plot: America's cheesiest dishes just got even cheesier and food obsessed is here to find them. We're piling our plates high with mounds of ooey-gooey goodness from all around the country.

4.title: Oodles of noodles
4.plot: Food obsessed is exploring the endless options for noodles. We've prepared our appetites for everything from noodles swimming in marinara sauce to noodles fried to perfection.

5.title: Franks for the memories
5.plot: Who needs a hamburger when you can have a hot dog? Food obsessed is searching high and low for hot dogs, frankfurters and sausages that will blow your mind.

6.title: How we roll
6.plot: From spring rolls and dinner rolls to rolling dough and rolling out the barrel, you won't believe what mouthwatering food is coming next. But hey, that's just how food obsessed rolls.

imdb.plot outline: Food lovers of the world unite. We're bringing our biggest appetites and digging into the world's tastiest meals for this ultimate guide to all things food. From master pizzas to oodles of noodles to deep-fried deliciousness and more, there's no need to hide your obsession with food -- we're here to celebrate it.
